--- Design
-------------------------------------------

In the beginning there was God, and a Node.js server hosting a single
static HTML page. However, this was no ordinary HTML page.


--- APIs/languages/tools used
-------------------------------------------

- Node.js
- JavaScript
- jQuery - AJAX
- HTML
- CSS
- BootStrap
- Facebook Graph API
- Bash scripting
- Arduino - servo hacking
- Python serial
- Physics
- Tkinter
- Twilio
- Google Voice
- JavaMail
- Android
- (PyALSA / PyALSAAudio)
- (NumPy for FFT frequency capturing)



